 * /hast/kobuki/cmd_vel [geometry_msgs/Twist]
 * /ardrone/navdata [unknown type]
 * /tf [tf2_msgs/TFMessage]
 * /tf_static [unknown type]
 * /hast/shutdown [hast/flag]
